{
  "stem": "27747.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were not very rich people, and they had to make a living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no pay, just food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And very possibly that they did not-- although they suspected I'm Jewish, maybe they made believe they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it is not easy to get a free mad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had not pleasant experiences, because the ones that were Ukrainian and their friends, they would say, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they always blocked it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They never made the comment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did not answer one way or the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they ignored her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she loved the little boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was a single woman, an old one, looked like a witch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she said that she takes care so well of the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who cares?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She would say.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My boss had a brother in the town of [INAUDIBLE]-- a brother with his wife and mother, and they were frequently visiting us with their two children.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The times when [INAUDIBLE] started to kill the Polish people, because they had a dream that they would get-- from the Germans, they would get an independent Ukraine after the war.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they figured if they do away with the Poles, they'll have less of a problem to accomplish that goal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this mother of my boss visited, and she told me that she knows I'm Jewish, she has a feeling I'm Jewish, and I should not tell the ones that I do not trust, but she's going to tell-- if I want to, I can tell myself to my boss, to her son, and to her other son.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They really did not comment one way or the other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was harvest time, and we helped out other families in the neighborhood-- Polish families that had also farms.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
